  "title": "Warehouse Admin cum Operations Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Warehouse Admin cum Operations Officer (Fulltime)</strong></p><p>Salary: $2500<br /><br /><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><p>·      Support daily operations and follow work procedures</p><p>·      Coordinate with customers and transporters for deliveries and collections</p><p>·      Help with order planning and shipment schedules</p><p>·      Pick, check, and pack items when needed</p><p>·      Assist with stock checks and cycle counts</p><p>·      Prepare shipment documents and simple reports</p><p>·      Ensure shipments are handled smoothly and ontime</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·      Comfortable with both admin and operations work</p><p>·      Able to communicate in English</p><p>·      Basic admin or warehouse experience is a plus</p><p>·      Warehouse system or MHE experience is anadvantage</p><p>·      Responsible, organized, and willing to learn</p>",
